content: प्रथित {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Increased, extended. {@--2@} Published, proclaimed, spread, declared; प्रथितयशसां भासकविसोमिल्लकविमिश्रादीनां <ls>M. 1.</ls> {@--3@} Shown, displayed, manifested, evinced. {@--4@} Famous, celebrated, renowned, wellknown; <ls>Pt. 1. 24</ls>; <ls>Ku. 5. 7.</ls> {@--5@} Intent upon, engaged in, devoted to. {@--6@} Spread, stretched. --तंः <ab>N.</ab> of Viṣṇu.
